## Step-by-Step Implementation

### Step 1: Create Parent Orchestrator Component

```vue
<template>
  <div ref="orchestratorRef" class="animation-orchestrator">
    <!-- Child components that will be coordinated -->
    <ChildComponentA />
    <ChildComponentB />
    <ChildComponentC />
