## Real-World Example: AiConductorGraphicV2

### Architecture Overview

**Component:** `src/components/vue/ui/AiConductorGraphicV2.vue`

**Structure:**
```
AiConductorGraphicV2 (Parent Orchestrator)
â”œâ”€ AnimatedFloatingElement (Wrapper)
â”‚  â””â”€ AiOrb (Child - pulses on events)
â”‚  â””â”€ SocialPathway Ã— 6 (Children - spark + pulse animations)
â”‚  â””â”€ ChatBubble (Child - cycles messages)
```

**Event Flow:**
```
1. Parent useRafFn loop calculates timing
2. Emits 'pathway-activate' at calculated intervals
3. Each SocialPathway listens for its index
4. Pathways trigger spark + icon pulse animations
5. ChatBubble cycles on 'bubble-cycle-start'
6. All stop on 'stop-all' event
```

### Key Implementation Details

**Parent Orchestrator (simplified):**
```typescript
const { pause: pauseRaf, resume: resumeRaf } = useRafFn(() => {
  if (!isViewportReady.value) {
    stopAnimation()
  } else if (!state.isPlaying && isComponentReady.value) {
    orchestrateAnimation()
  }
}, { immediate: false })

const orchestrateAnimation = () => {
  state.isPlaying = true

  const animateLoop = (currentTime: DOMHighResTimeStamp) => {
    const elapsedSinceCycleStart = currentTime - currentCycleStartTime!
    const cycleDurationMs = state.cycleDuration * 1000

    if (state.currentMode === 'rotation') {
      const providerCount = validatedProviders.value.length
      const timePerProvider = cycleDurationMs / providerCount

      validatedProviders.value.forEach((provider, index) => {
        const activationTime = index * timePerProvider

        if (elapsedSinceCycleStart >= activationTime &&
            elapsedSinceCycleStart < activationTime + timePerProvider) {
          bus.emit('pathway-activate', { index, provider, delay: 0 })
        }
      })
    } else {
      // Unison mode - all at once
      if (elapsedSinceCycleStart < 50) {
        validatedProviders.value.forEach((provider, index) => {
          bus.emit('pathway-activate', { index, provider, delay: 0 })
        })
      }
    }

    if (elapsedSinceCycleStart >= cycleDurationMs) {
      currentCycleStartTime = currentTime
    }

    animationFrameId = requestAnimationFrame(animateLoop)
  }

  animationFrameId = requestAnimationFrame(animateLoop)
}
```

**Child Listener (SocialPathway simplified):**
```typescript
const cleanupPathwayActivate = bus.on('pathway-activate', (data) => {
  if (data.index === props.index) {
    // Trigger spark animation
    sparkAnimation.play()

    // Schedule icon pulse
    setTimeout(() => {
      iconPulseAnimation.play()
    }, props.pulseDelay)
  }
})
```

### Performance Optimizations

1. **Triple-layer viewport detection:**
   ```typescript
   const elementVisible = useElementVisibility(conductorRef, { threshold: 0.1 })
   const documentVisible = useDocumentVisibility()
   const isViewportReady = computed(() =>
     elementVisible.value && documentVisible.value === 'visible'
   )
   ```

2. **RAF pause when offscreen:**
   ```typescript
   watch(isViewportReady, (ready) => {
     if (ready) {
       resumeRaf()
     } else {
       pauseRaf()
       stopAnimation()
     }
   })
   ```

3. **Prevent animation conflicts:**
   ```typescript
   const busEmitSafe = (eventName: string, data?: unknown, options?: { force?: boolean }) => {
     if (!isFloatingAnimating.value || options?.force) {
       bus.emit(eventName, data)
     }
   }
   ```

