2. **Elements** (13 composables) - DOM element interactions
3. **Sensors** (27 composables) - User input and device sensors
4. **Browser** (44 composables) - Browser APIs
5. **Watch** (11 composables) - Reactive watchers
6. **Reactivity** (15 composables) - Reactive helpers

